So, this behavior is basically correct, but we should remove all invalid columns before writing back to file.  The only problem I see is that Thellier GUI uses a few non MagIC column names (we just take them out in RmKeys in upload_magic).  So, we need to make sure we remove non-site columns except for any Thellier GUI specific internal columns.

